                        <Label fx:id="textWiki" prefHeight="100.0" prefWidth="640.0" text="Twonky is cute - by robot standards - and this is perhaps its greatest defense. From every angle, &#10;it appears friendly and unassuming, but Twonky is the kind of robot who kicks you hard in the shins&#10;with its titanium feet, giggles in a high-pitched voice that makes your ears ring for days, &#10;then runs away at a surprisingly high speed.">
